[[span class="lekton3"]]__[https://youtu.be/bc5Nk1DXyEY?t=55 Generals gathered in their masses...]__[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//The Engineer of the Chaos Insurgency has exactly six months, thirteen days, four hours and thirty-two minutes to live.//
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton"]]She has a plan.[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//Director Connor O’Malley of the US Paranatural Warfare Command watches a// //continent’s worth of flashing red lights blink off one by one.//
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton"]]He has a plan.[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//O5-6 sits atop a throne at the center of a conquered Hell and orders// //another twenty billion dollars worth of emergency assets liquidated.//
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton"]]He has a plan.[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//General Telemon Bowe shakes hands with a devil and watches the Council of 108 eat itself alive.//
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton"]]He has a plan.[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//Battle lines are drawn. Shallow caches are unearthed. Enmities centuries in the making bare envenomed teeth. The world hangs in the balance.//
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton"]] Just as planned.[[/span]]

[[div class="center"]]
//The woman formerly known as O5-7 casts an anxious look over her shoulder and flees onwards across the American West.// 
[[/div]]

[[span class="lekton2"]]
She really needs to come up with a plan.
[[/span]]

